the poseidon project ( also known as the poseidon project ) is a 2016 american science fiction action film directed by steven spielberg and produced by steven spielberg . it is the first film in the disaster film series . the film premiered at the 2015 toronto international film festival . the film was released in the united states on july 31 , 2016 . the film premiered at the toronto international film festival on september 8 , 2016 . the film received mixed reviews from critics .